steps:

1. File > New Project > Console Application.
2. Give a name "Palindrome"
3.Go to Pages Folder > index.cshtml
4. Code for index.cshtml :
@page
@model IndexModel

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Amity University</title>
    <style>
        .main-title {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: navy;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .description {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: purple;
            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .logo-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

            .logo-container img {
                height: 100px;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="logo-container">
        <img src="/images/amity-logo.jpg" alt="Amity Logo" />
        <div class="main-title">Amity University, Mumbai</div>
    </div>

    <div class="description">
        Amity University, Mumbai is situated in Bhatan, Panvel offers a variety of courses in Applied Sciences, I.T, Fashion Technology and many others.
    </div>

</body>
</html>


5. Go to wwwroot folder > Right click > make new folder and name it add "Images" 
6. Right click on Images folder > Add > Exsisting File  > select "amity-logo.jpg" 

7. run the file
